

                                      RELEASE CHECKLIST


  1. Tag the release commit:

      git tag -s vX.X.X

  2. Update the version in `.config/init.rx`
  3. Update the version in `src/main.rs`
  4. Update the version in Cargo.toml
  5. Push tags:

      git push --tags

  6. Publish crate:

      cargo package
      cargo publish
